channel.title: Help Logging into My Server!~ WILL REP++
channel.description: Hi, i'm having a problem logging into my server. Im hosting like i normally do, bittorent, and no-ip. But after i quit hosting for usman, i couldnt log onto my own server. Does anyone know how to fix this? or possibly get a new program to host? 'not utorrent..' Will REP++

item.title: Help Logging into My Server!~ WILL REP++
item.dc:creator: @usman555 usman555
item.description:
@usman555 wrote:

Redo the no-ip step in starting your own server. Get new server IP and change connecting IP addresses from server and client.
I managed to come back onto UsmanIsland after you left.
